### Test Simple AI (No Context)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/simple?query=Why is the Payment Processing system failing, and who should I contact?
Accept: application/json

### Test In-Context Learning (Prompt Stuffing)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/in-context
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "query": "Why is the Payment Processing system failing, and who should I contact?",
  "context": "Ticket-102: The Payment Gateway service is currently experiencing latency due to a downstream failure in the User Database. Contact the Backend Platform Team."
}

### Standard RAG Endpoint
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rag?query=Why is the Payment Processing system failing, and who should I contact?
Accept: text/plain

### GraphRAG Endpoint
GET http://localhost:8080/api/graphrag?query=Why is the Payment Processing system failing, and who should I contact?
Accept: text/plain
